{"tid":1563903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Popo同消防不停強調831太子站無死人其實喺捉字塞？","createTime":"2019-09-12T14:36:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T12:51:31.000Z","uid":70100,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"634f33f414668731e21c266fef78ae5179f17691","tid":1563903,"uid":70100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:36:44.000Z","msg":"//覺得d popo 同消防 係咁話831太子站無死人， 其實喺度捉字塞。 可能在太子站未死， 運到去第二個到就救唔返死咗。 <br />\n<br />\n推到有記者手足代問 : <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1) **831 當晚 (即31/08 晚上 及 01/09 零晨）， 全港港鐵站內、相關運送車內、醫院警處有否死人？**  <br />\n<br />\n2) 黨鐵請交哂全部被封站的cctv 出來，讓畫面講出真相。 </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n** 唔交出cctv 原因， 可能封站後d 死傷者比d 9 虐打得好勁。播出嚟又多個核彈。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8c59917039994957a4d00bc4b5914b203185417b","tid":1563903,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:37:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"9ca2e4b2b37cde81bf5bd119fa290a1616626f65","tid":1563903,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig